131
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:24,009
And old temple near
Kyoto station.

132
00:14:24,009 --> 00:14:29,965
It's tha best season to enjoy
autumn leaves in Kyoto.

133
00:14:29,965 --> 00:14:36,565
